Class AccumuloBackedCorpus

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.jhu.rebar.accumulo.AccumuloBackedStagedDataCollection
      • edu.jhu.rebar.accumulo.AccumuloBackedCorpus
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Corpus, StagedDataCollection

    public class AccumuloBackedCorpus
extends AccumuloBackedStagedDataCollection
implements Corpus
    Accumulo-backed implementation of the Corpus interface. This class should not be directly instantiated; use Corpus.Factory.getCorpus() instead.
